      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I have a job for you now. All you need to do is gather up a few materials. What do you think? Do you want to do it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Drop by every once in a while, and I’ll have some work for you. What do you think? Isn’t that cool? Valen’s been trying to come up with new dishes lately, and it seems he needs more fresh ingredients… Bring me #b10 each of #t4000061#s, #t4000031#s, #t4000032#s, and #t4000040#s#k. What do you think?"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Oh, really? Well, it's not something I need right this minute, so take your time, see if you want to do it. If you do, then come talk to me, alright? Well, I gotta get going..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Did you gather them all up? Let's see..."
