        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "As usual!! You’re as accurate as ever! You really handle tasks better than anyone I’ve seen so far. If something comes up again someday, I think I’ll be able to count on you. And as a reward, I’ll let Uncle #p112# at #m10000000# know so you can come to #m10007000# for free anytime from now on. See you around~"
        }
